msgid "Staff Professional Development Fund"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/staff/professional-development-policy.md:5
msgid ""
"The Carpentries staff have access to a professional development fund "
"(hereon after \"Staff PDF\") of $1000/year for each full time employee."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/staff/professional-development-policy.md:7
msgid "What Activities are Eligible?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/staff/professional-development-policy.md:9
msgid ""
"The Staff PDF makes available funds for the purpose of supporting staff "
"participation in professional development programs such as workshops and "
"seminars and research activities."
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/staff/professional-development-policy.md:11
msgid ""
"Requests must demonstrate how the activity for which funding is sought "
"supports the:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/staff/professional-development-policy.md:13
msgid "Current Strategic Plan for The Carpentries;"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/staff/professional-development-policy.md:14
msgid "Employee's Individual Professional Development:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/staff/professional-development-policy.md:15
msgid "Through improving performance in the employee’s current position; or"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/staff/professional-development-policy.md:16
msgid ""
"Through improving the employee’s qualifications for career opportunities "
"that may arise within The Carpentries"
msgstr ""

#: ../../handbook/topic_folders/policies/staff/professional-development-policy.md:18
msgid ""
"When applying for reimbursement for professional development materials or"
" activities, staff should provide a short description and justification "
"of the expenditure. For large expenses (>$200), staff should seek prior "
"approval from the Finance subcommittee."
msgstr ""

